{% extends "layout_project.njk" %}
{% block content %}
    {% from "_components.njk" import iframeVideo %}
    <div class = "text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">Sumo Fighting Robot</h2>
        <p class="item-intro text-muted">Project in grade 9 Robotics Club</p>
    </div>
    <!-- https://www.w3schools.com/bootstrap/bootstrap_carousel.asp
                    https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.0/components/carousel/ -->
    <div id="carouselSumoBot" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <!-- Indicators -->
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselSumoBot" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselSumoBot" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        </ol>
        <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="../img/portfolio/sumobot/IMG_20150625_215507_SumoSide.jpg" alt="Chicago"
                        class="d-block w-100 portfolioImgWide">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p>Side view</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="../img/portfolio/sumobot/IMG_20150625_215523_sumoFront.jpg" alt="Chicago"
                        class="d-block w-100 portfolioImgWide">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p>Front view</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- Left and right controls -->
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselSumoBot" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselSumoBot" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="portfolio-description">
        <p>Our robotics club teacher, <a href="https://www.siriusmicro.com/index.html">Mr. Rampelt</a>,
            organized a sumo fight competetion. The aim was to make a robot that pushes your oponents robot off
            the platform. I used a Ultrasonic sonar module to detect the other robot, and then push it off the edge by
            driving forward.
            This was the project I created in Robotics Club that sparked my interest to create all my other
            projects. It senses the edge of the table (using IR), and objects in front of it (with sonar).
        </p>
        <p>
            Below is a demo of the robot sensing objects infront of it, and the edge of a table to avoid
            falling off.
        </p>
        {{ iframeVideo("a8SXxGuowEE") }}
        <p>
            The next video is the competition between my robot and my teacher's.
        </p>
        {{ iframeVideo("H1_DfjgdxdI") }}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
        <ul class="list-inline">
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/AbhinavA10/" target="_blank">Github Repo</a>
            </li>
            <li>Timeframe: Grade 9</li>
            <li>Relevant Technologies: C</li>
        </ul>
        <a  href="../projects.html">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button">
                <i class="fa fa-times"></i>
                  Close Project
            </button>
        </a>
    </div>
{% endblock %}